---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="Power Apps Development | Julius Bruch"
    description="Custom Canvas and Model-driven applications to digitize and optimize your business processes. Expert Power Apps development services by Julius Bruch."
>
    <main>
        <!-- Service Detail Section -->
        <section class="project-detail">
            <div class="container">
                <a href="/#services" class="back-link">
                    <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i>
                    <span data-en="Back to Services" data-de="Zurück zu Dienstleistungen">Back to Services</span>
                </a>

                <div class="project-detail-content">
                    <div class="project-detail-header">
                        <h1 data-en="Power Apps Development" data-de="Power Apps Entwicklung">Power Apps Development</h1>
                        <p class="project-category" data-en="Canvas Apps | Model-driven Apps | Portals" data-de="Canvas Apps | Model-driven Apps | Portals">Canvas Apps | Model-driven Apps | Portals</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="project-detail-image">
                        <div class="image-placeholder" aria-hidden="true">📱</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="project-detail-body">
                        <h2 data-en="Service Overview" data-de="Leistungsübersicht">Service Overview</h2>
                        <p data-en="I build custom Canvas and Model-driven applications to digitize and optimize your business processes. Whether you need a mobile inspection app for field workers or a complex back-office system to replace legacy software, Power Apps provides a rapid development environment that connects seamlessly to your data." data-de="Ich entwickle maßgeschneiderte Canvas- und Model-driven-Anwendungen, um Ihre Geschäftsprozesse zu digitalisieren und zu optimieren. Egal, ob Sie eine mobile Inspektions-App für Außendienstmitarbeiter oder ein komplexes Backoffice-System als Ersatz für Altsoftware benötigen, Power Apps bietet eine schnelle Entwicklungsumgebung, die sich nahtlos mit Ihren Daten verbindet.">I build custom Canvas and Model-driven applications to digitize and optimize your business processes. Whether you need a mobile inspection app for field workers or a complex back-office system to replace legacy software, Power Apps provides a rapid development environment that connects seamlessly to your data.</p>
                        <p data-en="I follow professional Application Lifecycle Management (ALM) practices, utilizing separate development, testing, and production environments to ensure the highest quality, secure deployments, and stability for your enterprise applications." data-de="Ich arbeite nach professionellen Application Lifecycle Management (ALM) Standards und nutze strikt getrennte Entwicklungs-, Test- und Produktionsumgebungen, um höchste Qualität, sichere Deployments und Stabilität für Ihre Unternehmensanwendungen zu gewährleisten.">I follow professional Application Lifecycle Management (ALM) practices, utilizing separate development, testing, and production environments to ensure the highest quality, secure deployments, and stability for your enterprise applications.</p>

                        <h2 data-en="Licensing Information" data-de="Lizenzinformationen">Licensing Information</h2>
                        <p data-en="Understanding Power Apps licensing is crucial for planning your project budget. Licensing primarily depends on the data sources (connectors) your app needs:" data-de="Das Verständnis der Power Apps-Lizenzierung ist entscheidend für die Planung Ihres Projektbudgets. Die Lizenzierung hängt in erster Linie von den Datenquellen (Konnektoren) ab, die Ihre App benötigt:">Understanding Power Apps licensing is crucial for planning your project budget. Licensing primarily depends on the data sources (connectors) your app needs:</p>
                        <ul class="features-list">
                            <li data-en="Standard Connectors: If your app only uses standard connectors (like SharePoint, OneDrive, and basic Microsoft 365 services), usage is typically included at no extra cost in your existing Microsoft 365 Business or Enterprise plan." data-de="Standard-Konnektoren: Wenn Ihre App nur Standard-Konnektoren (wie SharePoint, OneDrive und grundlegende Microsoft 365-Dienste) verwendet, ist die Nutzung in der Regel ohne zusätzliche Kosten in Ihrem bestehenden Microsoft 365 Business- oder Enterprise-Plan enthalten."><b>Standard Connectors:</b> If your app only uses standard connectors (like SharePoint, OneDrive, and basic Microsoft 365 services), usage is typically included at no extra cost in your existing Microsoft 365 Business or Enterprise plan.</li>
                            <li data-en="Premium Connectors: To connect to premium sources like SQL Server, Dataverse, Salesforce, or custom APIs, you will need a standalone Power Apps license." data-de="Premium-Konnektoren: Um eine Verbindung zu Premium-Quellen wie SQL Server, Dataverse, Salesforce oder benutzerdefinierten APIs herzustellen, benötigen Sie eine eigenständige Power Apps-Lizenz."><b>Premium Connectors:</b> To connect to premium sources like SQL Server, Dataverse, Salesforce, or custom APIs, you will need a standalone Power Apps license.</li>
                            <li data-en="Per App Plan: Ideal for businesses that want to license users for specific apps only. Costs roughly $5 per user/app/month." data-de="Pro-App-Plan: Ideal für Unternehmen, die Benutzer nur für bestimmte Apps lizenzieren möchten. Kostet etwa 5 $ pro Benutzer/App/Monat."><b>Per App Plan:</b> Ideal for businesses that want to license users for specific apps only. Costs roughly $5 per user/app/month.</li>
                            <li data-en="Per User Plan: Best if your users need access to multiple premium apps. Costs roughly $20 per user/month." data-de="Pro-Benutzer-Plan: Am besten geeignet, wenn Ihre Benutzer Zugriff auf mehrere Premium-Apps benötigen. Kostet etwa 20 $ pro Benutzer/Monat."><b>Per User Plan:</b> Best if your users need access to multiple premium apps. Costs roughly $20 per user/month.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Contact CTA -->
            <section class="contact-cta">
                <div class="container">
                    <h2 data-en="Ready to build your app?" data-de="Bereit, Ihre App zu erstellen?">Ready to build your app?</h2>
                    <p data-en="Let's discuss your requirements and find the best architectural and licensing approach." data-de="Lassen Sie uns Ihre Anforderungen besprechen und den besten Architektur- und Lizenzierungsansatz finden.">Let's discuss your requirements and find the best architectural and licensing approach.</p>
                    <a href="/#contact" class="cta-button" data-en="Get in Touch" data-de="Kontaktieren Sie mich">Get in Touch</a>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
</Layout>